longBusinessSummary: Ajmera Realty & Infra India Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the real estate development business in India. It constructs and develops residential and commercial projects. The company was founded in 1968 and is based in Mumbai, India. Ajmera Realty & Infra India Limited is a subsidiary of Ariil Trust.
